rolled mug rather than pouring toohottodrink coffee into a paper cup or travel mug then impatiently waiting until the temperature falls to a comfortable drinking level and soon thereafter to an unpleasant lukewarm ember will rapidly cool your hot coffee or tea down to a chosen temperature and will hold it at that exact temperature for hours on end “i started ember to solve a simple yet universal challenge faced by coffee and tea drinkers everywhere  how can i keep my hot beverage at the ideal temperature for as long as i want” said ember technologies founder and ceo clay alexander “the release of ember is seven years in the making and it’s inspiring to see the caliber of investors we have attracted” about ember ember plans to revolutionize the way the world eats and drinks founded in  by inventor and serial entrepreneur clayton alexander ember has built an incredible team of worldclass product designers and engineers formally with nokia microsoft and amazon labs with big plans to transform the drinkware and dishware industry for more information please visit our website at wwwembertechcom media contact mark riedy marktrueoverdrivecom 4   source true overdrive on behalf of ember technologies inc share on facebook share on twitter categories business news business to business tags demi lovato ember ember technologies fundraising funding investor joe jonas nick jonas additional images about true overdrive view website we are a media relations company dedicated to driving exposure for brands in the active outdoor wearable technology and consumer electronics sectors we deliver results that help achieve business success for our clients more press releases ember earns top honors for its sleek design at the  idsa idea awards temperature control innovator recognized at the international design excellence awards idea in the kitchen  accessories category true overdrive  jun   ember technologies releases the worlds first temperature adjustable mug true overdrive  nov   ember te