cific features what is the rapidcooling technology ember has the ability to rapidly cool to the perfect temperature you choose the patented phase change cooling system allows scorching hot liquids to cool at a faster rate to your desired temperature does ember work for cold drinks too the ember mug will not actively refrigerate a cold beverage for long periods it will keep the contents cold like any other thermos would but ember was specifically designed to rapidly cool scolding hot liquid can the mug switch between fahrenheit and celsius yes you can switch between fahrenheit and celsius using the settings icon on the ember app what type of battery does my ember use the ember uses a standard lithium ion battery specifically designed for providing the best energy efficiency for an amazing user experience is there a car charger unfortunately not yet we have definitely plans to launch a car charger compatible for your ember while we want you to have the best experience with ember and its potential to charge on the go we do not have      support topics getting started faq troubleshooting care  maintenance email us still having problems reach out to us here search here en results found do these help 34cbe7cd474ccbemberdeskmailcom httpscdndeskcom false desk loading seconds ago a minute ago minutes ago an hour ago hours ago a day ago days ago about false invalid characters found customerenportalarticlesautocomplete read article ffffff pagetopic ember technologies inc true ember technologies inc company profile  bloomberg feedback ember technologies inc private company company profile sector industrials industry engineering  construction svcs subindustry engineering services ember technologies inc was founded in  the companys line of business includes providing professional engineering services corporate information address 44 newby rd madison al 37 united states phone  fax  from the web sponsored financial commentaries more from the web home news top headlines most popular